parameters.name: AclName
parameters.description: The name of the ACL. The name must be 1 to 30 characters in length, and can contain letters, digits, periods (.), hyphens (-), forward slashes (/), and underscores (\_). The name must be unique within the region.

parameters.name: AddressIPVersion
parameters.description: The IP version. Valid values: **ipv4** and **ipv6**.
